# Walkthrough: pipeline/graph/ LangGraph Orchestration

## What Was Built

The complete `pipeline/graph/` module — the heart of the Research Pilot pipeline. It wires every previously-built module (models, DB ORM, events, telemetry, exceptions, config) into a compiled LangGraph `StateGraph` with 8 nodes and conditional routing edges.

