## Graph Topology

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    __start__ --> ingest
    ingest --> classify
    classify -->|confidence ≥ 0.5| extract
    classify -->|confidence < 0.5| __end__
    extract -->|success| summarise
    extract -->|failed| __end__
    summarise --> embed
    embed --> diagram
    diagram -->|has architecture| codegen
    diagram -->|theory domain| report
    codegen --> report
    report --> __end__
```

