## Usage

```python
from pipeline.graph import research_pipeline, make_initial_state

# PDF upload path
state = make_initial_state(
    run_id="my-run-001",
    pdf_bytes=open("paper.pdf", "rb").read(),
)
result = research_pipeline.invoke(state)

print(result["domain"])          # e.g. "Computer Vision"
print(result["report_path"])     # Supabase Storage path
print(len(result["summaries"]))  # 4

# arXiv path — provide metadata with arxiv_id
from pipeline.models.paper import PaperMetadata
state = make_initial_state(
    paper_metadata=PaperMetadata(title="Attention Is All You Need", arxiv_id="1706.03762"),
)
result = research_pipeline.invoke(state)
```
